    "location_state": "TX",
    "method_used": "PicoSure",
    "review_text": "My only regret is not starting sooner. After years of struggling with severe razor burn, ingrown hairs, and \"strawberry legs\" that resisted every traditional hair removal method, my physician recommended laser treatment. Following thorough research, I chose LaserAway.\nThe experience was seamless from the start. The initial consultation was informative, and the team provided a flexible payment plan that made the procedure truly affordable. The facility is clean, easy to find, and offers a welcoming, high-end atmosphere.\nI cannot thank my nurse, Ms. T, enough. She was professional and incredibly friendly, ensuring I was comfortable throughout the appointment. I was shocked by how painless the process was; in fact, the environment was so calming that I nearly dozed off.\nThank you, Ms. T and LaserAway, for a transformative and professional experience!",
